# RGB Sliders
Simple RGB color controller built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features
- Adjust red, green, and blue channels individually
- See live color preview
- Reset colors to default
- Increment/decrement values using buttons

## Future Improvements
- Add color history or palette
- Enable copy-to-clipboard functionality

## Next Step
- Implement async copy-to-clipboard for HEX and RGB codes

